# {{projectName}}

This is an API Platform project created with the MultiTech CLI using Docker.

## Requirements

- Docker
- Docker Compose

## Installation

1. Clone this repository
2. Run `docker-compose up -d` to start the containers
3. Access the API at http://localhost:8000

## Usage

### Development

```bash
# Start the containers
docker-compose up -d

# Stop the containers
docker-compose down

# View logs
docker-compose logs -f
```

### API Documentation

The API documentation is available at:
- [API Platform UI](http://localhost:8000/api)
- [Swagger UI](http://localhost:8000/api/docs.json)

### Database

The MySQL database is accessible at:
- Host: localhost
- Port: 3306
- Database: api
- Username: api
- Password: api

## Features

- [API Platform](https://api-platform.com/) for building API-first applications
- [Symfony](https://symfony.com/) as the underlying framework
- [Doctrine ORM](https://www.doctrine-project.org/projects/orm.html) for database access
- [JWT Authentication](https://jwt.io/) for secure API access
- Docker for easy setup and deployment

